Package fr.softsf.sudofx2024.interfaces.mapper

Interface IBackgroundMapper

public interface IBackgroundMapper
This interface defines methods for mapping objects of type Background to objects of type BackgroundDto and vice versa. It uses MapStruct to automatically generate the implementations of these mapping methods.

  • Field Summary

    Modifier and Type
    Field
    Description
    static final IBackgroundMapper
    INSTANCE
    This instance is created by MapStruct and provides access to the mapping methods defined in this interface.
